channel.title: Wilderness Zone Help
channel.description: I need help on adding wildy, for example varrock except bank. And how to make it so that players has these 'wildy indicators' in lower right corner (just like allstar, it says wildy or safe). I need help with teles too, how i make custom teles that tele in custom locations underground like mage bank? if a thread excists, which could help me, please post it.

item.title: Wilderness Zone Help
item.dc:creator: @de_dust89 de dust89
item.description:
@de_dust89 wrote:

Dude A LOT of tutorials on this… search bar is ftw. =p

and for the custom teles. teleport to the spot you want to go… (like click the lumby tele) and get the coords u landed on, then go into clickingmost.java and search the first coord, if the second coord matches, then edit the coords to where you want to go, and boom lumby tele teles you to mage bank =o
